":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/KSHM/111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c285%2c20220321%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"KSHM,111,聲,285,20220321,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"285","JDATE":"20220321","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}